    "updated_at": "2014-02-12T11:19:43Z",
    "body": "I would have assumed that given the option of removing all uses of globs, versus removing solely `pub use` globs, that the latter would be the far more attractive option in most projects.  But perhaps I am mistaken.\n\n(edit: I speak solely in terms of pain of doing the transformation; I am not speaking on the quality of the code after the transformation, since one can reasonably claim that a codebase with no globs of any kind is easier to work with.  Not that _I_ am claiming that... :) )\n",
