    "updated_at": "2014-02-27T07:35:16Z",
    "body": "This sounds like a very reasonable proposal. I'm against glob imports for production code, but for tests they're great (e.g. pulling in all the names of the module you are testing). Re-exporting everything from a different module sounds like a recipe for disaster on the user-facing side even if it worked correctly in the compiler. \n\n+1 for preventing people from shooting themselves in the foot.\n",
